flowchart TD
    User[Config Studio User] --> ALB[ALB / DNS endpoint]
    ALB --> GW[API Gateway<br/>512MB / 0.5 vCPU<br/>Route adapter + Auth + Circuit Breakers]
    
    GW -->|sync HTTP| VS[Validation Service<br/>1GB / 0.5 vCPU<br/>Validate, Compare, Search, Promote]
    GW -->|sync HTTP| RS[Refund Service<br/>2GB / 1 vCPU<br/>Export orchestration + Streaming]
    
    VS -->|HTTP| CS[wdpr-config-services<br/>Java persistence layer]
    RS -->|HTTP| CS
    
    VS -->|publish events| SNS[payment-controls-events<br/>SNS Topic]
    RS -->|publish events| SNS
    
    SNS -->|filter: export.*| SQS1[validation-events-queue<br/>SQS]
    SNS -->|filter: config.*| SQS2[refund-events-queue<br/>SQS]
    
    SQS1 -->|poll| VS
    SQS2 -->|poll| RS

    style GW fill:#4a9eff,color:#fff
    style VS fill:#28a745,color:#fff
    style RS fill:#fd7e14,color:#fff
    style CS fill:#6c757d,color:#fff
    style SNS fill:#ff6b9d,color:#fff